706997f-b.title: Brooklyn: Surf Ave. - 20th St. W.
706997f-b.text:
(1)
Surf Ave., north side, west from the N.E. eorner of West 20th Street,
showing in order the Carmen's Sylvia Inn and Restaurant (N.E. eorner) and
Busoni's Danceland (N.W. corner).
January 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2)
The sawe, a closeup of Busoni'e Danceland.
